text: Oghna, also Ogna, is a village in Jhadol tehsil, Udaipur district, Rajasthan, India. It is mostly dependent on agriculture. ==Sources== * Udaipur.Rajasthan.gov.in - Blocks, Tehsils, Panchayats * Census of India 1961: vol XVI - Rajasthan (pdf) Category:Villages in Udaipur district
title: Oghna
